# PEP 561 marker — maya_py ships inline type information. Presence of this file
# tells mypy / pyright / Pylance to trust this package's annotations: the native
# extension is described by the hand-maintained _maya.pyi stub, and the pure
# Python modules (easy.py, widgets.py, program.py, pixels.py) carry inline
# annotations. Editors get completion + type-checking across the whole surface.
